		<div id="comment_body_64967515">Carrots alone does not work. See also CEO pay linked to company performance,. What is needed is both a carrot and a stick. The CEO equivalent would be, if the company does badly the CEO loses his house and/or personally pays for company debt.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64967515">

